{"type": "article", "id": 7694, "title": "Timeburner 运动手表", "description": "", "date": "2015-03-24T07:03:37Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234515onIPAWKiE0FOyqUb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t在瑞士举办的 Baselworld 手表珠宝展览会上，Miki Eleta 带来了他的作品，这款名为 Timeburner 的运动手表。这款手表的设计灵感来自于摩托车的发动机，是对早起内燃机的致敬：铝制的活塞代替了指针，机械运动驱动活塞，推动着齿轮旋转，同时又指示着秒数。这款手表每一款都限量生产，只有99个，三种颜色可选，分别是银白色 （silverlight），铬黄骑士色（chrome-rider）和全黑色（all-black）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234514Fl7Rx2S0nuc3qhIt.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.74572127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234514TFnxw6sp9WVuQ0AN.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234514zOjP8qsd5wZBxtUb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.73716381\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}